### search offers (browse mode)
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/offers/search

### fuzzy search - typo tolerance
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/offers/search?searchText=coiffur

### fuzzy search with category
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/offers/search?searchText=tresse&category=HAIR_BEAUTY

### fuzzy search with location
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/offers/search?searchText=coiffeuse&latitude=50.0782&longitude=8.2398&radiusKm=20

### create offer
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/offers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "I offer beauty services for all of you in wiesbaden and around (20km around)",
  "title": "Tresses à Domicile",
  "category": "HAIR_BEAUTY"
}

### get offer
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/offers/d50a8041-3149-4f5a-8f89-4e3c76e0dfbe
Content-Type: application/json

### update offer
PUT {{apiBaseUrl}}/offers/d50a8041-3149-4f5a-8f89-4e3c76e0dfbe
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "description": "I offer beauty services for all of you in wiesbaden and around (20km around)",
  "title": "Tresses à Domicile",
  "category": "HAIR_BEAUTY",
  "price": 30, "promotionalPrice": 20,
